5762_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zhORkRHeefkQ7kNvgHvA9rk&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AZq8Se-P3RWr9axmbgae_zE&oh=00_AYD7VbztNc3rjNS3ja0rvG8YfY4QVz53RU8Pqe-gtCjBiA&oe=66E41B92"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "landscape2_2560x1440.png", "id": "1426934824544087", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031561_1426934827877420_6410939235148926638_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tQUJVpMk5h8Q7kNvgHtq1vI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AZq8Se-P3RWr9axmbgae_zE&oh=00_AYAlKzOWn7au0daqC3ClOkjbCaOVVzwgDPb3FfHpLn72TQ&oe=66E40732"}, "display_name": "Ready. Aim. Dodge! Dodgeball-Archery Fusion", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Everyone's favorite sports have finally gotten a mashup!\n\nTest your skill and fitness levels as you battle for the leaderboard in this family-friendly fusion of dodgeball and archery. How long can you hold out against the barrage of canon-fired balls?\n\nSee how your archery skills stack up as you try to earn the title of Top Shot in a distance shooting competition!\n\nBattle with friends or against them in 2-4 player private and public matches, co-op and PVP!  (Multiplayer matches require an internet connection.)\n\nFirst level of Tower Defense Campaign 1 DLC now included! Protect the townspeople from dodgeball wielding robots as you hone your archery skills!", "short_description": "Everyone's favorite sports have finally gotten a mashup!\n\nTest your skill and fitness levels as you battle for the leaderboard in this family-friendly fusion of dodgeball and archery. How long can you hold out against the barrage of canon-fired balls?\n\nSee how your archery skills stack up as you try to earn the title of Top Shot in a distance shooting competition!\n\nBattle with friends or against them in 2-4 player private and public matches, co-op and PVP! (Multiplayer requires internet)"}]}, "developer_name": "Motor City Code Factory, LLC", "developer_privacy_pol